{"tid":50981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中印買家搶購　Bitcoin創近兩年新高","createTime":"2016-12-23T00:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T03:19:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d73d78d9ff8bbf260887ed528cc9eaa64c374581","tid":50981,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"中印買家搶購　Bitcoin創近兩年新高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n■Bitcoin周三最高升見874美元，創近兩年最高。資料圖片<br />\n【本報綜合報道】虛擬貨幣Bitcoin被炒起！Bitcoin周三最高升見874美元，創近兩年最高，主因中國和印度買家搶購Bitcoin務求資產保值。<br />\n<br />\n受內地走資潮和人民幣持續貶值影響，內地大媽追買Bitcoin避險。據Coindesk資料顯示，Bitcoin昨日曾見874.1美元，為2014年1月以來最高。歐洲交易時段，Bitcoin升幅略為收窄至857.96美元，升2.98%，成交額高達137.7億美元（約1,067億港元）。Bitcoin兌人民幣亦創新高，升至6,171.87人民幣，較美元計價溢價約2%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，印度買家為應對政府廢除大額面鈔，也加入搶購Bitcoin。印度虛擬貨幣交易平台Zebpay顯示，Bitcoin價格高見1,020美元，較美元計價溢價約14%。<br />\n<br />\n虛擬貨幣價格比較網站CryptoCompare創辦人Charles Hayter表示，此輪Bitcoin升勢突破心理關口，中國買家在近日整體交易佔大多數。他估算今年10月至11月高峯期，中國每日平均多達1,000萬枚Bitcoin成交，料現時中國每日成交量回落至約350萬枚。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19874047&amp;category_guid=15307&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19874047%26category_guid%3D15307%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161223&d=ZHGxvMuO0tRv%2B7Y2z5pkRZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a7780628\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19874047%26category_guid%3D15307%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161223&h=3304b6fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19874047&amp;category_guid=15307&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161223</a>"},{"pid":"908e0c43f53c36b2c0c5b322b31287b93751f562","tid":50981,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:17:51.000Z","msg":"回一回會逐啲逐啲買黎草"},{"pid":"d8426d9b2db636dc9c265cb89310430ab678f2ca","tid":50981,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12